text: Agdistopis griveaudi is a moth in the Macropiratidae family. It is known from Madagascar.Gibeaux, C. 1994b. Insectes Lépidoptères: Pterophoridae. - Faune de Madagascar 81. CIRAD - 81:1–176 ==References== Category:Macropiratidae Category:Moths of Madagascar Category:Moths of Africa
